# Day 1, workshop 1 - setting up project
# Setup up the course example project

- [x] 1. Git repo: https://github.com/Plepic-OU/classroomio/
  - [x] 1a. Use HTTPS, we need this later.
  - [x] 1b. Git clone https://github.com/Plepic-OU/classroomio.git
- [x] 2. Create a personal branch
- [x] 3. Install docker if not installed
- [x] 4. Install npm if not installed
- [x] 5. Install devcontainer (https://github.com/devcontainers/cli)
- [x] 6. Run the devcontainers, see project README.md
- [x] 7. Log into devcontainers and start “cskip” - claude without permissions check.
  - [x] 7a. Authenticate claude and answer questions
- [x] 8. Run the “/init” to get personal CLAUDE.md file

Optional
